These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, techno, ambient, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, malaysian, polish, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, swimming, golf
1. the spanish is the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
3. the argentine is in an odd position##4
4. the polish is not the fan of jazz##6
5. the person who's sport is swimming is not the spanish##6
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the argentine##3
7. the argentine is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the malaysian##7
8. the person who's sport is soccer is between the fan of techno and the fan of ambient##2
9. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | punk      | techno   | jazz  |
| Nationality   | spanish    | polish   | argentine | malaysian  |
| Sport         | golf | soccer | swimming     | lacrosse |

