.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, tea, coffee
There 4 different types of food: orange, cranberry, lime, grapes
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, american, australian, russian
 1. the person eating grapes is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating orange is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking tea is not the person eating cranberry##6
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person eating lime##1
 5. the person eating orange is the australian##1
 6. the person eating lime is the russian##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the american##1
 8. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the american##3
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person drinking tea##7
10. the australian is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | soy-milk         | tea    | coffee  |
| Food          | grapes     | cranberry | orange | lime |
| Nationality   | argentine     | american     | australian  | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, skydiving, drawing, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, indonesian, italian, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, ship, snowmobile
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
4. the spanish is between the indian and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the indonesian##7
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby         | chess | drawing  | skydiving  | singing |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | italian | spanish | indian     |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | motorbike     | roller     | ship         |

