There are 4 different nationalities: thai, malaysian, polish, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, bus, roller
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the malaysian is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the fan of country is the person driving the boat##1
5. the polish is the fan of dubstep##1
6. the thai is the person driving the bike##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
8. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the fan of country and the fan of r&b##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | country    | disco     | dubstep   | r&b      |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | thai | polish | australian  |
| Transport     | boat | bike  | roller    | bus |

