The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, rock, dubstep, folk
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, goat, hedgehog
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the fan of folk##6
2. the fan of rock is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the fan of funk##7
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person drinking tea##7
5. the person drinking tea is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the goat is the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the fan of funk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea  | hot-chocolate | mirinda | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | folk | dubstep  | rock  | funk    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | ferret  | goldfish    | goat    |

