The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, collecting, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, canadian, indian, pakistani
1. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
3. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
4. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking juice##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person drinking water is not the spanish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | water | juice        | milk       |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking    | card-games | sudoku |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | canadian  | spanish    | indian   |

