4 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, ferret, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
3. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the ferret##2
4. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
5. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
7. the firefighter is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the helicopter##7
8. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
9. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
| Job         | software-developer | firefighter | dressmaker    | analyst |
| Pet         | chinchilla      | snake | turtle       | ferret         |
| Transport   | snowmobile | boat    | roller | helicopter     |

