The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, time-travel, fantasy, comedy
4 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
 1. the owner of the mouse is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 7. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching comedy movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | baking | magic-tricks      | card-games | cooking |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | time-travel | animation  | comedy       |
| Pet           | turtle         | mouse       | hamster    | guinea-pig  |

