4. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person eating cucumber##7
5. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
7. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
8. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
9. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

