4. the fan of disco is on the right of the polish##1
5. the fan of house is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
6. the chinese is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
7. the chinese is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is cycling##7
8. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the fan of folk is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is skiing##7

