.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, water, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, japanese, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, subway, bus, snowmobile
 1. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the bus is between the mexican and the japanese##2
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the spanish##5
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 7. the mexican is not the person drinking 7up##6
 8. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking water##7
 9. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
11. the indonesian is between the japanese and the mexican##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water | hot-chocolate     | 7up      | almond-milk     |
| Nationality   | spanish  | mexican   | indonesian   | japanese |
| Transport     | snowmobile     | trike | bus | subway   |

