.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-14::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, spinach, pomegranate, eggplant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, jazz, punk, folk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, rugby, basketball
1. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the fan of folk##7
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the fan of jazz##7
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
4. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
8. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
9. the person who's sport is rugby is not the fan of ambient##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | grapes | eggplant | pomegranate          | spinach  |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | ambient      | jazz    | folk   |
| Sport         | swimming | biathlon  | rugby | basketball |

