4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
5. the person eating peas is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
6. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating peas##1
7. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
8. the person watching musical movies is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
9. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food          | zucchini   | broccoli  | peas     | kale    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | musical | family      | action |
| Sport         | swimming | cycling     | baseball | surfing       |

