The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, engineer, bartender, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, time-travel, mystery, martial-arts
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
2. the coach is not the person watching mystery movies##6
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left or far right##3
9. the bartender is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the coach##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | filmmaking   | skydiving | reading |
| Job           | engineer     | writer | bartender   | coach |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel         | mystery        | action  | martial-arts   |

