 4. the owner of the horse is not the person watching superhero movies##6
 5. the teacher is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the rat##7
 6. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the electrician is the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher | accountant | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | musical     | spy      | animation    |
| Pet           | frog    | rabbit      | rat     | horse  |

 